00:14:04.660 --> 00:14:09.080
And now do we want to bend the bezel
in over it just a little bit to hold it better.

00:14:09.080 --> 00:14:11.560
&gt;&gt; So, this is call it burnishing tool,

00:14:11.560 --> 00:14:15.580
and what we use this
for is to bend that brass

00:14:15.580 --> 00:14:17.860
over the top of the stone like that

00:14:17.860 --> 00:14:18.920
